title: A House is Not a Home
description: Sabrina Marshall is an ambitious senior in high school was just after she just became a cheerleader and made honor roll for the first time. She's so excited for her life to begin until it all comes crashing down with a tragedy that changes the course of her life forever. When her responsibilities shift and her home is taken away from her, she now has to navigate how she's going to take care of herself and her two little siblings. She leaves that a physical house is not a home.
author: S.T. Jones
